---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Know Your Water"
  description="Scan a QR code on your MiMaji water bottle to instantly see the source, quality test results, treatment process, and delivery date. Water transparency for every household in Nairobi and beyond."
  ogImage="/mimaji-water-bottle-with-qr-code-label.png"
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">Water Transparency</div>
    <h1>Know Your <em>Water</em></h1>
    <p>Every drop you drink should come with a story. Scan the QR code on your MiMaji water bottle and instantly see exactly where your water came from, how it was treated, and how it tested.</p>
    <svg class="hero-wave" viewBox="0 0 1440 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,60 C360,100 720,20 1080,60 C1260,80 1380,50 1440,60 L1440,100 L0,100Z" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </section>

  <!-- Hero image -->
  <section class="bottle-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="bottle-grid fade-in">
        <div class="bottle-content">
          <div class="section-label">Why It Matters</div>
          <h2>Most Kenyans Don&rsquo;t Know What&rsquo;s in Their Water</h2>
          <p>Across Nairobi, millions of households buy water from informal vendors, kiosks, and delivery services every day &mdash; with no way to verify quality, source, or treatment. We change that with a single scan.</p>
          <p>Every <a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MiMaji</a> bottle and refill carries a unique QR code. Scan it with your phone and you instantly know everything about that exact batch of water &mdash; before you drink it.</p>
          <a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Order MiMaji Water &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bottle-visual">
          <img
            src="/mimaji-water-bottle-with-qr-code-label.png"
            alt="MiMaji 20L water bottle with QR code label showing serial number for water source verification"
            loading="lazy"
            width="400"
            height="600"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How it works -->
  <section class="bg-sand">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">How It Works</div>
      <div class="section-title">Three Steps to Total Transparency</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">Scanning a MiMaji QR code takes seconds and works on any phone &mdash; no app download required.</div>

      <div class="how-grid fade-in">
        <div class="how-image">
          <img
            src="/qr-code-how-it-works.png"
            alt="Step-by-step illustration of how the MiMaji Know Your Water QR code system works for verifying water quality"
            loading="lazy"
            width="800"
            height="500"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="how-steps">
          <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-num">01</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Find the QR code</h4>
              <p>Every MiMaji water bottle, jerrycan, and refill container carries a unique QR code label with a serial number. Look for it on the side of the bottle.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-num">02</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Scan with your phone</h4>
              <p>Open your phone&rsquo;s camera and point it at the code. No app download needed. The link opens directly in your browser.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step-item">
            <div class="step-num">03</div>
            <div>
              <h4>See your water&rsquo;s full story</h4>
              <p>Instantly view the source, treatment, quality test results, and delivery date for that exact batch &mdash; verified and timestamped.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What you see -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">In the App</div>
      <div class="section-title">Everything You Need to Trust Your Water</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">When you scan a MiMaji QR code, here&rsquo;s what your phone shows.</div>

      <div class="info-grid fade-in">
        <div class="info-content">
          <div class="info-feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">◉</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Water Source</h4>
              <p>The exact borehole, refinery, or treatment plant your water came from &mdash; with location and operator details.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">◆</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Treatment Process</h4>
              <p>How the water was purified: filtration, reverse osmosis, UV, mineralisation. Full process disclosure, every batch.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">▲</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Quality Test Results</h4>
              <p>TDS readings, pH levels, microbiological test results, and the date of the most recent quality check.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">●</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Batch & Delivery Date</h4>
              <p>When the water was bottled, who delivered it, and how fresh it is &mdash; right down to the timestamp.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">↗</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Vendor Verification</h4>
              <p>Confirm your delivery rider is a verified <a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MiMaji partner</a> &mdash; not someone reselling unknown water.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">★</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Report Issues</h4>
              <p>Tasted off? Container damaged? Report directly through the scan page &mdash; the MiMaji team responds within hours.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-image">
          <img
            src="/qr-code-app-information.png"
            alt="MiMaji Know Your Water app screen showing detailed water source, treatment, and quality information after QR code scan"
            loading="lazy"
            width="500"
            height="700"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Before & After Impact -->
  <section class="bg-sand">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">The Impact</div>
      <div class="section-title">Before MiMaji vs. After MiMaji</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">QR-coded water transparency changes the relationship between households and their water supply &mdash; from blind trust to verified confidence.</div>

      <div class="impact-image fade-in">
        <img
          src="/qr-code-before-after-impact.png"
          alt="Before and after impact of using the MiMaji Know Your Water QR code tool — showing the shift from unknown water sources to verified, transparent quality"
          loading="lazy"
          width="1000"
          height="600"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="ba-grid fade-in">
        <div class="ba-card before">
          <div class="ba-tag">Before</div>
          <h4>Blind Trust</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>No idea where the water came from</li>
            <li>No quality testing visible to consumer</li>
            <li>Vendors can&rsquo;t be verified</li>
            <li>Bottles refilled with unknown water</li>
            <li>No accountability when things go wrong</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="ba-card after">
          <div class="ba-tag">After</div>
          <h4>Verified Confidence</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Source, treatment, and quality on every bottle</li>
            <li>Real-time TDS and microbiological data</li>
            <li>Verified MiMaji vendors only</li>
            <li>Tamper-evident packaging and seals</li>
            <li>Direct line to report and resolve issues</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why this matters for the Foundation -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Foundation Connection</div>
      <div class="section-title">Why MiMaji Foundation Champions This</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">Water transparency isn&rsquo;t just a product feature &mdash; it&rsquo;s a public health intervention. We believe every household deserves to know what&rsquo;s in their water.</div>

      <div class="why-grid fade-in">
        <div class="why-card">
          <h4>Public Health</h4>
          <p>Waterborne diseases kill thousands of children every year in Sub-Saharan Africa. Most of these deaths come from water that was never tested. QR-verified water makes contamination traceable and preventable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <h4>Consumer Power</h4>
          <p>When residents can verify quality before drinking, they reward suppliers who do the work. The market shifts toward safer water for everyone &mdash; including the most vulnerable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <h4>Data for MajiMap</h4>
          <p>Aggregated, anonymised scan data feeds into <a href="/majimap/">MajiMap</a> &mdash; showing water quality patterns across Nairobi. Every scan strengthens the collective picture of water in our city.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <h4>Accountability</h4>
          <p>QR codes create a permanent record. If a batch fails quality testing later, every household that received it can be notified instantly. This is what real water safety looks like.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="section-title">Ready to Know Your Water?</div>
    <p>Order MiMaji-verified water for your home, office, or event. Every bottle carries a QR code. Every scan is a step toward water transparency for all.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-white">Order on MiMaji.co.ke &rarr;</a>
      <a href="/majimap/" class="btn btn-outline">Explore MajiMap</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .bottle-section {
    padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;
  }

  .bottle-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .bottle-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .bottle-content p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .bottle-content a:not(.btn) {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .bottle-visual {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .bottle-visual img {
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.18);
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  /* How it works */
  .how-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .how-image img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.12);
  }

  .how-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.8rem;
  }

  .step-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--blue);
    background: var(--blue-light);
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    min-width: 56px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .step-item h4 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .step-item p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Info features */
  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .info-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.4rem;
  }

  .info-feature {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    min-width: 44px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--blue-light);
    color: var(--blue);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .info-feature h4 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .info-feature p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .info-feature a {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .info-image img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.12);
  }

  /* Before / After */
  .impact-image {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .impact-image img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1000px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.12);
  }

  .ba-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .ba-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .ba-card.before {
    border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
  }

  .ba-card.after {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--teal);
  }

  .ba-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .ba-card.before .ba-tag {
    background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1);
    color: #dc3545;
  }

  .ba-card.after .ba-tag {
    background: rgba(26, 158, 143, 0.1);
    color: var(--teal);
  }

  .ba-card h4 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .ba-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .ba-card ul li {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    padding: 0.4rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.4rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .ba-card.before ul li::before {
    content: '✕';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #dc3545;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .ba-card.after ul li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--teal);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Why this matters */
  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .why-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .why-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.08);
  }

  .why-card h4 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .why-card p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .why-card a {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .bottle-grid,
    .how-grid,
    .info-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .ba-grid,
    .why-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
